, and make all the probes your lil heart desires.  <br /><br />It is such a misconception that HP = your effectiveness.  Its all about Focus and Mana Regen.  Sure you are not as effective with 1000hps compared to ~2000 hps.  But lets face it tier 3, or even tier 2, you get aggro and you dont A) FD instantly if unsnared, B) Get distance fast if mob is snared.  Then your dead within 3 rounds 75% of the time.  <br /><br />So you keep your extra 1000 base hps, and go tank soem golems or guardians.  Cause thats like 1 extra round of combat, which doesn't make one difference when your stunned. <br /><br />Don't get me wrong More of anything = better. (int/mana/hps/focus etc..)  But mana and mana regen are WAY more important after you hit certain "break" points now a days.  (focus effects naturally fit in with mana regen)<br /><br />Solo is just nowhere near like it was. You cannot live through 5 rounds of combat or off tank something for a tick or two.  Its just not an option.  So many people are stuck in the level 40's mentallity.  <br /><br /></span></font></td>
