aren't the way to go for you.  If you ever come to realize that a Necromancer is best played at 50-80% damaged then you'll realize that HP's are King (non-raid situations mind you, raid at 50% health can lead to instant death).<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /></span></font></td>
